{"id": 1664, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心xTechcare】为了和在乎的人（物）好好相处，你都做过哪些努力？", "description": "啊，这种一点点为梦想准备的过程，真的是甜蜜又艰辛啊。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 8024, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201705031733534Z8skc7JzSi0qPIu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-08T03:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 202070, "content": "为她戒了lol", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025056}, {"id": 201984, "content": "从一个极度鄙视韩剧的人变成爱看韩剧…现在回想真的是疯了…疯…了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013103}, {"id": 201985, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170509080800M6zagYJ5vkNwemZp.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 201731, "content": "做红烧茄子给她吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022701}, {"id": 201990, "content": "改掉坏脾气 好好和他说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668363}, {"id": 203270, "content": "在对自己好和他之间纠结犹豫了很久  最后选择了他", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991412}, {"id": 201735, "content": "想近一切办法了解她的一切，自己一屁股问题没解决，确热衷于解决她的问题。哎，想想感觉自己变了一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026307}, {"id": 201736, "content": "多和他聊天，关心他体贴他但是他没有喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001404}, {"id": 203016, "content": "每天充点气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029859}, {"id": 203528, "content": "改变自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980484}, {"id": 201737, "content": "因为爱而讨好，为了不被讨厌而讨好，为了融入而讨好。我都试过，但是当我没有在做自己的时候，我不开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994895}, {"id": 202249, "content": "从23名考到第一名", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975984}, {"id": 202505, "content": "学会变成对方喜欢的模样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984412}, {"id": 201739, "content": "忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 201996, "content": "容忍她的各种举动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984880}, {"id": 201741, "content": "变得有耐心", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026445}, {"id": 201743, "content": "早睡早起，少玩手机多看书，健康饮食，锻炼身体，不给自己找不痛快", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927985}, {"id": 201744, "content": "请他们吃东西，这是金牛座为了融入团队所能做的最好一步了。", "image": "img/option/option/201705081504550y4J1FHtGhWVkOgp.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774494}, {"id": 202000, "content": "变的温暖无比，无时无刻不传递正能量！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026520}, {"id": 202001, "content": "从高冷硬生生变得幽默风趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993137}, {"id": 203025, "content": "1嘴贱 听了难受 当做没听见\n2讲了ex多好多好 也告诉自己不要生气\n3让干嘛干嘛 都随他\n4总之 就是没脾气对这个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029869}, {"id": 201746, "content": "把自己变得更好，曾经他喜欢生活中的我，现在变得让他在工作上也离不开我", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026461}, {"id": 202002, "content": "高中时候的男友，每天上午给他写早安纸条，去餐厅买吃的会给他带。         但还是没能好好相处，分手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768915}, {"id": 201747, "content": "为了和在乎的人，能携手下去，逼迫自己变成更好的自己，慢慢去磨平年轻气盛的棱角，慢慢筛光无所在乎的杂质。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026429}, {"id": 202003, "content": "适当的装傻 适当的聪明", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025031}, {"id": 202259, "content": "装做若无其事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168760}, {"id": 202516, "content": "委屈自己，讨好别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028808}, {"id": 207380, "content": "放弃休息时间，跑到异地看他", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040326}, {"id": 201749, "content": "努力学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999324}, {"id": 202005, "content": "迁就、原谅", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422363}, {"id": 201750, "content": "让自己变的有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743215}, {"id": 202007, "content": "好好活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027077}, {"id": 202008, "content": "放下面子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741629}, {"id": 202009, "content": "实现她的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027102}, {"id": 201754, "content": "收起所谓的高冷和自尊，多表扬，发脾气之前数三秒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 202010, "content": "改变自己成为他喜欢的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623958}, {"id": 201755, "content": "学会笑而不语", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 202779, "content": "做了很多改变，惯着她", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029467}, {"id": 204315, "content": "情不知所起，一往而深\n学会耐得住寂寞，等他的一句话", "image": "img/option/option/201705162025117pmAlkdwaCrTzvny", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028228}, {"id": 201756, "content": "分手之后做朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892370}, {"id": 202012, "content": "退让和妥协了许多，做了当时不想要做或者不愿意做的许多事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252288}, {"id": 201757, "content": "已然变得没有自尊 没有脸面", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026494}, {"id": 202013, "content": "让学习充盈生活并赋予无穷的乐趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019548}, {"id": 201758, "content": "义务反顾理解支持。\n觉得他好 他什么都好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982015}, {"id": 202014, "content": "坚持 即使不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946145}, {"id": 201759, "content": "为了不影响男朋友的学习我我现在还没和他认识。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786396}, {"id": 202015, "content": "通常是我说十句 不见得回一句", "image": "img/option/option/20170509092406stlTdKUiPXbRVrL4", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672156}, {"id": 202016, "content": "学会换位思考。不足的地方学会反省。因为你的优秀所以要更加努力学习。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960142}, {"id": 201762, "content": "看各种段子，让无趣的自己显得不那么无趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894504}, {"id": 202018, "content": "迁就迁就再迁就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995420}]}